算法中的 3D 参数近似了从 3D 分布中采样的过程，解决了 DreamFusion 所提 SDS 算法的过饱和、过平滑、缺少多样性等问题。此外，SDS 往往需要很大的监督权重（CFG=100），而 VSD 是首个可以用正常 CFG（=7.5）的算法。无需任何3D数据，直接文本生成高质量3D内容，清华朱军团队带来重大进展_腾讯新闻"},"attached_info":"ClUI7KDbpLWcoepDEAMaCDk2NDA4ODQ3IM7Jz6MGMAQ46gFALnIJNjAzNTc3ODAxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y","detail_text":"26 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-27d4b953512e5511bc6156bf61605461_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"47_1685358900.5181172","card_id":"Q_603592926","target":{"id":603592926,"title":"我国将适时发射扩展舱段，未来空间站基本构型将由「T」字型升级为「十」字型，对我国航天事业意味着什么？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/603592926","type":"question","created":1685325849,"answer_count":51,"follower_count":102,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[24600,33652,57106,105508,153160],"comment_count":3,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"中国载人航天工程办公室副主任林西强表示，我国正在研制可重复使用的新一代近地载人运载火箭和新一代近地载人飞船。为进一步支持在轨科学实验、为航天员的工作和生活创造更好的条件，将适时发射扩展舱段，将空间站基本构型由“T”字型升级为“十”字型。新华社分享页"},"attached_info":"ClQI7KDbpLWcoepDEAMaCDk2NDEyMjAzIJmQ0KMGMAM4ZkAvcgk2MDM1OTI5MjZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I=","detail_text":"26 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-59b87e494123a221de196be6cd9ac973_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"48_1685358900.5191026","card_id":"Q_466341366","target":{"id":466341366,"title":"游戏《魔兽世界》有什么让你破防的瞬间？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/466341366","type":"question","created":1624261313,"answer_count":339,"follower_count":436,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[253,358,1608],"comment_count":7,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"at